They're both very haunted books that
-- you mentioned that and I thought

00:09:46.650 --> 00:09:47.950
when you said it I
thought, "Of course.

00:09:47.950 --> 00:09:50.860
Yes. These are both books that
are very concerned with -- ."

00:09:50.860 --> 00:09:52.200
[thumping sound] Oh, sorry.

00:09:52.200 --> 00:09:55.770
I just -- I gestured [laughing] so
excitedly I banged my microphone.

00:09:55.770 --> 00:09:57.280
These are both books
that are concerned

00:09:57.280 --> 00:09:58.640
with various kinds of haunting.

